Julie PFALTZGRAFF, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
IOWA DEPARTMENT OF HUMAN SERVICES, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-0189 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 19, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Julie Pfaltzgraff's appeals the district court ruling denying her petition for judicial review. AFFIRMED IN PART, REVERSED IN PART, AND REMANDED.

AFFIRMED IN PART IN PART, REVERSED IN PART, AND REMANDED.
